title: How do I clear my browser's cache and browsing history?
answer:
On the home screen, touch ![](http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/36a2a_ck4xv.png)Browser > ![](http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/36a2b_hgz8q.png) > More > Settings > Privacy & security, and follow the onscreen instructions.
